PROJECT DESCRIPTION - BENNET

OVERALL INTENTION:
An application that helps the user to cultivate healthy, life-supporting habits, in an easy & natural way.


' GOAL - SETTING ' 
The user defines one+ goal(s) he has.
Then he chooses habit(s) to work towards that goal on a daily basis.
AI will log the habits of every user in one vector database,
to give the user recommendations / ideas for new habits if desired.


' habit - REFLECTION ' 
He chooses a convenient time / point in his routine where he logs his progress (daily).
He checks which habits he completed and which not, 
and also logs wether it was easy or he struggled with it.

(If he found himself to struggle,
he can choose to talk to an 'AI-habit-Coach' that supports him in making 
small adjustment in his habit or the way he approaches it, 
to make it more easy and natural.)*


' habit - LOG '
The user has the ability at any time to see the progress he made in the past week
in a simple overview. 



